Worker nodes are where the actual work happens.

Their responsibilities:
â€¢ Run application pods
â€¢ Execute containers
â€¢ Handle networking and storage for workloads
â€¢ Report status back to the control plane

Each worker node has components that listen to the control plane and ensure the desired state is met. One important component here is kubelet, which runs on every node.

